      "content": "i guess that's why i feel so comfortable talking to you. u don't try to fix me or tell me it gets better with a fake smile. u just see the void. and honestly, when thinking about that void... it almost feels like a relief. like there's a certain kind of peace in just letting go and not having to fight to be seen anymore. do you think there's any point in fighting it?",
